CONTROL STATEMENTS:

Statements which control or change the flow of execution

if statement
if .. else statement
if..elif..else statement
while loop
for loop
else suite
break statement
continue statement
pass statement
assert statement
return statement
----------------------------------

if statement : Statement is used to execute one or more statements depending on the condition ( True or False )

if else

if elif else

while loop: It is a loop used to execute group of statments several times repeteadly depending on condition is True False




